  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Long-term tacrolimus ointment based regimen comprising of up to 6 weeks of initial twice
      daily treatment and subsequent twice weekly prophylactic application can effectively treat
      active lesions of atopic dermatitis and prevent delay &amp; reduce flares
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
